Name Rascal/Libraries/LabeledGraph/bottom

Function set[&T] bottom(LGraph[&T] G)
Description Returns the bottom nodes of LabeledGraph G, i.e., the leaf nodes that don't have any descendants.
Examples 
rascal>import LabeledGraph;
ok
rascal>bottom({<1,"A",2>, <1,"B",3>, <2,"C",4>, <3,"D",4>});
set[int]: {4}
